## Layouts

### Game layout pattern (fixed background)
```tsx
// app/dark-souls/layout.tsx — Server Component
export default function DarkSoulsLayout({ children }: { children: React.ReactNode }) {
  return (
    <div className="relative min-h-screen">
      <div className="fixed inset-0 -z-10">
        <Image src="/ds1-bg.jpg" alt="" fill priority className="object-cover opacity-30" />
      </div>
      {children}
    </div>
  );
}
```

### Root layout
`app/layout.tsx` includes: font variables, `<SiteHeader>`, `<AppMotionConfig>`.
Do not duplicate these in nested layouts.

---

## Images — next/image

### Rules
- Always `next/image`. Never `<img>` or CSS `background-image` in components.
- `fill` + `object-cover` for full-bleed backgrounds.
- `priority` on every image above the fold.
- Always provide `sizes` — directly affects LCP.

### Patterns
```tsx
// Full-bleed background (above fold)
<div className="relative w-full h-screen">
  <Image src="/inicio.png" alt="" fill priority sizes="100vw" className="object-cover" />
</div>

// Card image (below fold)
<div className="relative w-full aspect-[3/4]">
  <Image
    src="/character.jpg"
    alt="Artorias the Abysswalker"
    fill
    sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 1024px) 50vw, 25vw"
    className="object-cover object-top"
  />
</div>
```

