## Data Fetching

### Server Component (preferred)
```tsx
export default async function CharactersPage() {
  const { data: characters } = await supabase
    .from("characters")
    .select("*")
    .eq("game", "dark-souls");

  return <CharacterGrid characters={characters} />;
}
```

### Client-side (only when necessary)
Use only for: real-time data, user-specific data post-auth, or data dependent on client state.

