## Metadata
```tsx
// Static
export const metadata = {
  title: "Dark Souls — Soulspedia",
  description: "Lore archive for Dark Souls.",
};

// Dynamic
export async function generateMetadata({ params }: { params: { slug: string } }) {
  return { title: `${params.slug} — Soulspedia` };
}
```

---

## Game Route Pattern
Every game follows this exact structure — replicate, never invent a new one:
```
app/
└── [game-slug]/
    ├── layout.tsx        ← fixed bg image, Server Component
    ├── page.tsx          ← GameHubLanding, Server Component
    ├── characters/
    │   └── page.tsx      ← LoreCard grid, async data fetch
    └── forum/
        └── page.tsx      ← placeholder or Supabase threads
```

---

## Common Mistakes to Avoid
- ❌ `useRouter` or `useSearchParams` in Server Components → add `"use client"`
- ❌ Missing `priority` on hero/background images → LCP regression
- ❌ `<img>` instead of `next/image`
- ❌ Fetching inside Client Components when a Server fetch is possible
- ❌ `"use client"` on layout.tsx → breaks server rendering of children
- ❌ `getServerSideProps` or `getStaticProps` — App Router only, always
